name: I Have A Really Bad Feeling About This
Lore: '''I''m rather embarrassed, General Solo, but it appears you are to be the main course at a banquet in my honor.''',
Text: 'If opponent just initiated a battle where opponent has more than double your power, target your highest-ability character in that battle. Draw destiny. If destiny < target''s ability, deploy one character there from hand (for free).',
